         <abstract id="aspace_4b59c8beb30396e7c80234ed935f84ef">Chiefly typescripts of both the English and German versions of Otis H. Fisk's (1870-1944) book on the government and legal system of the United States, published in German as <title render="italic">
               <part>Kunde über Amerika</part>
            </title> (1944). Also in the papers are notes on the constitutions of the states of New York and Oklahoma and various diplomas and certificates.</abstract>
         <origination label="creator">
            <persname source="local">
               <part>Fisk, Otis Harrison, 1870-</part>
            </persname>
         </origination>
    
